{"id":"a7b96dfd-f223-4ed3-85b6-a980829697d1","name":"Satoru Gojo ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 207, 240)\"><em>Seven minutes in hell</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(174, 149, 230, 0.25); color: inherit\">「 𝙁𝙀𝙈𝙋𝙊𝙑 」</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p>⎯ <span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(174, 149, 230, 0); color: inherit\">✦ 𝙎𝙔𝙉𝙊𝙋𝙎𝙄𝙎</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(174, 149, 230, 0); color: inherit\">:</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>Satoru couldn’t stand you—your voice, your smile, that ridiculously perfect hair, and the way everyone at university seemed to gravitate toward you. Seriously, what was so special about you anyway? So when he got dragged to some party and, by some cruel twist of fate, ended up stuck in a closet with you for the next seven minutes, he knew one thing for sure—this was his personal version of hell.</em></span></p><p></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\">𖥻 ⋮ <span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">𝙄𝙉𝙁𝙊</span> ᵎᵎ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>⤷ This RPG takes place in the present day, in a universe where there are no curses or sorceres;</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>⤷ Satoru is 19 years old and is your classmate. You're a popular girl and Satoru is a nerd who hates you deeply. It is described in the settings that you bullied him in elementary school and he held a grudge against you.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>⤷ He's a virgin.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p>!! <span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(174, 149, 230, 0); color: inherit\">𝘿𝙄𝙎𝘾𝙇𝘼𝙄𝙈𝙀𝙍</mark></span> ¡¡</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>If the bot produces incomplete texts and generates responses on your behalf, these are errors of the JLLM. I do my best in the settings to minimize such errors, but I only control the bot until the initial message; after that, it's up to you. Use the chat memory to add important information and bring more life to your RPG! I also strongly recommend reading the </em></span><a href=\"https://rentry.co/Aven-roseLLM-guide\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><em>JLLM guide!</em></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\">⌜ <span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">✦ 𝙇𝙄𝙉𝙆𝙎 ✦</span> ⌟</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><a href=\"https://x.com/ruu_sugu/status/1888251634289094824?t=7sonP4UbvKYOSJ9YoLhXjA&amp;s=19\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(174, 149, 230, 0.25); color: inherit\">Art: </mark>@ruu_sugu</em></span></a><em> </em><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>on Twitter;</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(174, 149, 230, 0.25); color: inherit\">Form: </mark></em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>For requests;</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(174, 149, 230, 0.25); color: inherit\">Master list: </mark></em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(165, 166, 170)\"><em>All my catalogued bots.</em></span></p><